| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2699 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e46c0a8f-380d-52d2-b85b-b825fd0c96b7"
